item.title: Key Mexico State Votes in Election Poised to Boost AMLO's Party
item.description: Key Mexico State Votes Boost AMLO’s Party Key Mexico state votes were held on Sunday, and the outcome was a boost for the ruling Morena party of President Andrés Manuel López Obrador. Polls had shown Morena leading in most of the races, including in the populous states of Mexico City and the State of Mexico.
